fallen pod and decided she had to have it. She tapped her comm unit to 
contact Mosquitor.
    "Mosquitor! Hurry to the new location of the fallen pod1 I will join you 
in a few moments. Be swift!" She emphisized. Now, she had to deal with the 
Maximals.
